# Tensient Conventions

- **Name**: "Tensient" (not "Tenscient" -- no "c")
- **No middleware.ts**: Next.js 16 deprecated it; use auth() in server components/API routes
- **No OpenAI**: Use Google Gemini 3 Pro (lib/ai.ts)
- **Terminology**: "Download" (manager input), "Unload" (IC input) -- never "rant" or "spew"
- **Context library**: Read promptfood/BOOTSTRAP.md first for full project context
- **Cost controls**: Every AI route must call checkUsageAllowed() before and logUsage() after
